00:11:30,724 --> 00:11:32,390
I needed something blue collar,

255
00:11:32,392 --> 00:11:35,226
 something my great-grandfather
   Preston would be proud of.

256
00:11:35,228 --> 00:11:37,729
         Society needed
      people contributing
      on the ground floor,

257
00:11:37,731 --> 00:11:40,131
         not middle men
