00:12:13,133 --> 00:12:14,265
         -I'll call...
      -(speaking Spanish)

274
00:12:14,267 --> 00:12:15,767
             -Okay?
          -Okay. Wow.

275
00:12:15,769 --> 00:12:18,103
          -All right.
      -(speaking Spanish)

276
00:12:18,105 --> 00:12:20,338
        That feels good
